Codes for replicating Figures 2 to 4 in:
"Optimal Quadrature Subsampling for Least Squares Polynomial Approximations"
Pranay Seshadri, Akil Narayan and Sankaran Mahadevan

Copyright (c) 2016 by Pranay Seshadri
Email: ps583 <at> cam.ac.uk

To get the exact results in the paper, this code requires the following packages:
1) Paul Constantine & David Gleich's parameterized matrix package (PMPack). Available at: http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/29228-pmpack-parameterized-matrix-package

2) Raymond Reynold's ciplot package. Available at: http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/13103-plot-confidence-intervals/content/ciplot.m


